SPECIAL NOTICE FOR ISLAMIC INHERITANCE CALCULATIONS:

This software is intended to assist Muslims in creating wills and calculating 
inheritance distribution according to Islamic principles. While every effort 
has been made to ensure accuracy according to general Islamic jurisprudence:

1. This software does not constitute religious or legal advice
2. Complex inheritance situations may require consultation with qualified Islamic scholars
3. Legal validity of wills varies by jurisdiction and local laws
4. Users are responsible for verifying compliance with local legal requirements
5. The author disclaims liability for any consequences arising from use of this software

For religious guidance, please consult qualified Islamic scholars.
For legal validity, please consult qualified attorneys in your jurisdiction.

May Allah bless this work and make it beneficial for the Muslim Ummah.